One of our customer is looking for developers to work in a combined role for DevOps and Configuration Management in a newly created Continuous Integration and Continuous Development team.

&#xa0;

Required skills:&#xa0;

- You need to have solid competence in both software development and operating system configuration.&#xa0;

Tooling:&#xa0;

- gitlab/gitlab-ci&#xa0;

- flow jira + confluence&#xa0;

- docker&#xa0;

- kubernetes&#xa0;

- java&#xa0;

- cucumber&#xa0;

- spinnaker&#xa0;

- AWS/Cloud

Guided by our global brand promise, PROTECTS WHAT´S GOOD, we strive to make a difference by protecting food, people and our futures. We need smart people too. People like you, who wants to work with people like us.

Through collaboration with the Data Science CoE you will deliver Advanced Analytics Use Cases

Global IM has approx. 

Analytics Use Cases are capitalising on this high volume of data and in collaborations with Tetra Pak’s Data Science CoE new insights and solutions are exposed to Customers, Internal Users and Applications. All done in adherence with the company IT Security Policy to keep the information safe and utilising role-based security to ensure proper access.

This position will be located in Lund. Travelling not more than 30 days per year is expected.&#xa0;



A dedicated team focused on delivering Analytics Use Cases together with the Data Science CoE.&#xa0;

 Primary capabilities around data onboarding/engineering and model deployment for the prioritised Use Cases.&#xa0;



 Backlog prioritisation is done together with Data Science CoE based on the pipeline of Use Cases.&#xa0;

What you will do

	Manage Deployment of Models in collaboration with Data Scientists
	Manage Deployment of other components (DB, APIs etc.) in Analytics Use Cases.

	Review and improve deployment process and tools

Who you are

	?Personal drive & problem-solving mentality&#xa0;
	Stakeholder management skills&#xa0;
	Ability to work across time-zones, culturally aware and able to collaborate with people from other countries.&#xa0;
	Team player – will collect and share information with colleagues in order to improve our services.&#xa0;
	Self-motivated and driven. Communicates and debates solutions to issues found. Proactively contacts colleagues or lead to work on problems or improvements.&#xa0;
	Azure DevOps&#xa0;
	ML Flow&#xa0;
	Experience from System Integration&#xa0;
	Experience in CI/CD and DevOps&#xa0;
	Experience from working with Azure implementations&#xa0;
	Python, automation and application&#xa0;

	A(zure)RM Templating&#xa0;
	Ansible/Terraform or any other orchestration&#xa0;

	Airflow - advantageous&#xa0;

	IP Networks, with experience debugging issues in DNS, HTTP&#xa0;

We offer

Join us to work with the latest cloud technologies in a dynamic and collaborative environment. Be part of Advanced Analytics use case delivery capitalising on Big Data in cloud whilst delivering real business value for Tetra Pak. Collaborate in a global context with customers, users and colleagues all over the world.

Care to join?

DETTA SÖKER VI

Du är en&#xa0;utvecklare&#xa0;som kan (nästan) allt om&#xa0;DevOps! Du är också himla bra på&#xa0;versionshantering&#xa0;och verktyg för detta.&#xa0;&#xa0;

CHECKLISTA FÖR SÖKANDE

Om det här är du:&#xa0;

Kan du arbeta&#xa0;agilt?&#xa0;

Har du minst två års erfarenhet som&#xa0;devops?&#xa0;

Har du jobbat med:&#xa0;

	Konfigurering&#xa0;
	Byggautomatisering&#xa0;
	Automatisk testning&#xa0;&#xa0;
	Systemadministration&#xa0;
	Configuration&#xa0;Management&#xa0;

Är du en mästare inom något av:&#xa0;&#xa0;

	Docker&#xa0;
	Kubernetes&#xa0;
	Linux, Windows eller Cloud&#xa0;
	Python,&#xa0;Javascript, Java, C/C++&#xa0;
	Jenkins, Maven,&#xa0;Gradie&#xa0;
	GIT, Clear Case, Artifactory&#xa0;

&#xa0;…så vill vi gärna ha dig som kollega!&#xa0;

DETTA FÅR DU

Du får ditt drömjobb på&#xa0;HiQ&#xa0;Göteborg, ett kommunikations- och teknikbolag med framåtanda och affärer från Kalifornien till Moskva.&#xa0;&#xa0;

Du får stöd av ett team av kollegor som kan lika mycket som du inom varierande områden.&#xa0;&#xa0;

Du får jobba med spännande uppdrag som verkligen gör livet lättare för folk.&#xa0;

Du får möjlighet att utvecklas som människa och som kollega, och bli bättre på det du redan är bäst på!&#xa0;Vi anställer personer med rätt attityd och kompetens och tror på att skapande och erfarenheter går hand i hand.&#xa0;
